(6, 7780, 'Erma Bombeck', 'niki@nikk.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:06:02', '2014-04-26 18:06:02', 'For years my wedding ring has done its job. It has led me not into temptation. It has reminded my husband numerous times at parties that it\'s time to go home. It has been a source of relief to a dinner companion. It has been a status symbol in the maternity ward.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(7, 7780, 'Jennifer Aniston', 'niki@nikk.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:07:00', '2014-04-26 18:07:00', 'One tradition I have with my friends is that when one of us gets married, we have a ton of fragrance oils and pretty bottles at the bachelorette party. Everyone puts a drop or two in a bottle for the bride and makes a wish, and the bride wears our creation on her wedding day.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(8, 7780, 'John Mayer', 'niki@nikk.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:07:41', '2014-04-26 18:07:41', 'A man\'s got two shots for jewelry: a wedding ring and a watch. The watch is a lot easier to get on and off than a wedding ring.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(9, 7780, 'Jane Seymour', 'niki@nikk.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:08:35', '2014-04-26 18:08:35', 'I think a lot of people get so obsessed with the wedding and the expense of the wedding that they miss out on what the real purpose is. It\'s not about a production number, it\'s about a meaningful moment between two people that\'s witnessed by people that they actually really know and care about.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(10, 7780, 'Ellie Goulding', 'niki@nikk.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:08:53', '2014-04-26 18:08:53', 'I met Prince William at a musical festival and he let me know he was a fan of my music. But the invitation to sing at his wedding reception came completely out of the blue. The fact that Kate and William knew the words to my songs was very touching.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(11, 7780, 'John Mayer', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:21:24', '2014-04-26 18:21:24', 'A man\'s got two shots for jewelry: a wedding ring and a watch. The watch is a lot easier to get on and off than a wedding ring.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nSRCpertZn8\" title=\"John Mayer - Who You Love ft. Katy Perry\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer ugc\">John Mayer - Who You Love ft. Katy Perry</a>', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(12, 7780, 'Gary Jones', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:21:51', '2014-04-26 18:21:51', 'Lorem ipsum is a pseudo-Latin text used in web design, typography, layout, and .... Select a text frame, then chose \"Sample Text\" from the context menu after ...', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(13, 7780, 'Groucho Marx', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:22:07', '2014-04-26 18:22:07', 'I was married by a judge. I should have asked for a jury.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(14, 7780, 'Jane Seymour', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.90.12.15', '2014-04-26 18:22:18', '2014-04-26 18:22:18', 'I think a lot of people get so obsessed with the wedding and the expense of the wedding that they miss out on what the real purpose is. It\'s not about a production number, it\'s about a meaningful moment between two people that\'s witnessed by people that they actually really know and care about.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(15, 7780, 'Gary Jones', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:36:25', '2014-05-02 15:36:25', 'For years my wedding ring has done its job. It has led me not into temptation. It has reminded my husband numerous times at parties that it’s time to go home. It has been a source of relief to a dinner companion. It has been a status symbol in the maternity ward.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(16, 7780, 'Jane Seymour', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:37:26', '2014-05-02 15:37:26', 'I think a lot of people get so obsessed with the wedding and the expense of the wedding that they miss out on what the real purpose is. It’s not about a production number, it’s about a meaningful moment between two people that’s witnessed by people that they actually really know and care about.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(17, 7780, 'Ellie Goulding', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:39:05', '2014-05-02 15:39:05', 'I met Prince William at a musical festival and he let me know he was a fan of my music. But the invitation to sing at his wedding reception came completely out of the blue. The fact that Kate and William knew the words to my songs was very touching...', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(18, 7780, 'Socrates', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:39:52', '2014-05-02 15:39:52', 'My advice to you is get married: if you find a good wife you\'ll be happy; if not, you\'ll become a philosopher.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(19, 7780, 'George Sands', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:40:19', '2014-05-02 15:40:19', 'There is only one happiness in life,\nto love and be loved.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(20, 7780, 'Ralph Block', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:40:42', '2014-05-02 15:40:42', 'You\'re nothing short of my everything.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(21, 7780, 'Anonymous', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:41:04', '2014-05-02 15:41:04', 'ove is like playing the piano.\nFirst you must learn to play by the rules,\nthen you must forget the rules\nand play from your heart.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(22, 7780, 'Michael Leunig', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:41:24', '2014-05-02 15:41:24', 'Love one another and you will be happy.  It\'s as simple and as difficult as that.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(23, 7780, 'Maxwell Anderson', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:41:40', '2014-05-02 15:41:40', 'If two stand shoulder to shoulder against the gods,\nHappy together, the gods themselves are helpless\nAgainst them while they stand so.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(24, 7780, 'Thomas Lovell Beddoes', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:42:02', '2014-05-02 15:42:02', 'Tell me how many beads there are\nIn a silver chain\nOf evening rain,\nUnravelled from the tumbling main,\nAnd threading the eye of a yellow star: -\nSo many times do I love again.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(25, 7780, 'Antonio Hurtado de Mendoza', 'junk@vamtam.com', '', '78.128.102.133', '2014-05-02 15:42:22', '2014-05-02 15:42:22', 'Think not because you are now wed\nThat all your courtship\'s at an end.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
