(11881, 1, '2020-02-02 11:32:45', '2020-02-02 11:32:45', '[column width=\"1/5\" title=\"undefined\" title_type=\"undefined\" animation=\"from-right\" implicit=\"true\"]\n\n [services fullimage=\"false\" icon=\"css3\" icon_color=\"accent3\" icon_size=\"16\" background=\"accent1\" image=\"\" title=\"Revolution Slider\" text_align=\"left\" button_link=\"#\" button_text=\"\"]\nThe premium Revolution slider - $18 value . [push h=\"5\"] <a href=\"#\">Read More</a> [icon name=\"theme-angle-right\" style=\"\" color=\"accent2\" size=\"8\" ]\n\n [/services]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width=\"1/5\" title=\"undefined\" title_type=\"undefined\" animation=\"from-right\" implicit=\"true\"]\n\n [services fullimage=\"false\" icon=\"theme-brush\" icon_color=\"accent3\" icon_size=\"16\" background=\"accent1\" image=\"\" title=\"Easy Styling\" text_align=\"left\" button_link=\"#\" button_text=\"\"]\n1200 Premium Icon Set – $39 Value!.. [push h=\"5\"] <a href=\"#\">Read More</a> [icon name=\"theme-angle-right\" style=\"\" color=\"accent2\" size=\"8\" ]\n\n [/services]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width=\"1/5\" title=\"undefined\" title_type=\"undefined\" animation=\"fade-in\" implicit=\"true\"]\n\n [services fullimage=\"false\" icon=\"copy3\" icon_color=\"accent3\" icon_size=\"16\" background=\"accent1\" image=\"\" title=\"Drag &amp; Drop Builder\" text_align=\"left\" button_link=\"#\" button_text=\"\"]\nThe theme uses a flexible template builder that enables you to create unique pages and posts. [push h=\"5\"] <a href=\"#\">Read More</a> [icon name=\"theme-angle-right\" style=\"\" color=\"accent2\" size=\"8\" ]\n\n [/services]\n\n [/column]\n\n [column width=\"1/5\" title=\"undefined\" title_type=\"undefined\" animation=\"from-left\" implicit=\"true\"]\n\n [services fullimage=\"false\" icon=\"cart-checkout\" icon_color=\"accent3\" icon_size=\"16\" background=\"accent1\" image=\"\" title=\"WooCommerce Shop\" text_align=\"left\" button_link=\"#\" button_text=\"\"]\nSupport for the great plug