(11937, 1, '2020-02-02 13:45:46', '2020-02-02 13:45:46', 'Honestly, the best mechanics I’ve ever been to. They give you a recommendation of what needs to be fixed or to take it as-is for what you dropped the car in for. Highly recommended. I love the work!', 'Alison M', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'alison-m', '', '', '2020-02-02 13:45:46', '2020-02-02 13:45:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kelvin_grove/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=11937', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0),
(11938, 1, '2020-02-02 13:47:10', '2020-02-02 13:47:10', 'I absolutely love the people and services provided by the Kelvin Grove Tyres and Mechanical! They have gone above and beyond for me and my car more than once. I trust everything they say, but they always show me photos and take the time to explain everything to me in a way I can understand. I would 100% recommend to anyone looking to get a really reliable service. Thanks so much to the Kelvin Grove Tyres and Mechanical Team!!!', 'Shane M', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shane-m', '', '', '2020-02-02 13:47:10', '2020-02-02 13:47:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kelvin_grove/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=11938', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0);
